    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A forbidden act of bodily sacrifice. When you fail a Fortitude saving throw against poison or disease, you may immediately spend Chakra. Your new result equals 2 times the Chakra spent (no bonuses added unless you have Mastery).</p>\n<p><b>Mastery Progression:</b></p>\n<p>Step 3 Mastery: Add your Constitution modifier to the final result.</p>\n<p>Step 5 Mastery: Add your full Fortitude bonus to the final result. (Replaces Step 3; they do not stack.)</p>\n\n",
